NAME
     nneedd - full-screen editor with windows

SYNOPSIS

     nneedd [[ffiillee__nnaammee]]

DESCRIPTION

     The nneedd macro runs the editor with the same name in a sub-shell.  It is the
     editor of choice for the developers of ssppeecc.

     The source code to nneedd is available by request from Certified Scientific
     Software, but comes with no guarantees.

DEFINITION

     ddeeff nneedd ''uunniixx((""nneedd $$**""))''

EXAMPLE

     nneedd mmyy..mmaacc

